  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to assess the efficacy and safety of using combination of 755-nm picosecond&#xD;
      alexandrite laser and 2% hydroquinone compared with 2% hydroquinone alone for the treatment&#xD;
      of melasma: A randomized split-face controlled trial&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
